{"tid":2185394,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[FUCK HARDER] 車路士以史上最貴球員身價簽入球員Harder","createTime":"2020-09-02T08:36:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T00:54:59.000Z","uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"33fe8d84761585065c3ffbcd4c0222823a690eb2","tid":2185394,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T08:36:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2020/09/02/f/f487002e0371044512d2ae60712371f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2020%2F09%2F02%2Ff%2Ff487002e0371044512d2ae60712371f4.jpg&h=04350753&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n車路士於今個轉會窗動作頻頻，已經先後簽入華拿、捷維爾、薛耶治等實力戰將，原來在女足隊他們也有重大收購，以破紀錄價錢簽入丹麥女足射手赫達 ( Pernille Harder ) ，刷新女子足球員的轉會費紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n車路士女足日前宣佈，從禾夫斯堡女足簽入赫達，轉會費為 35 萬歐元，打破兩年前中國球隊江蘇蘇寧女足以 14.3 萬歐元簽入塔希塔 ( Tabitha ) 的紀錄。赫達接受球會訪問時表示十分高興加盟車路士，期待為球隊效力。<br />\n<br />\n27 歲的赫達於 2017 年加盟禾夫斯堡女足，合共上陣 114 場比賽，攻入 105 球，曾帶領球隊四奪聯賽冠軍，又試過在三年內兩度進入歐聯決賽，包括上季不敵里昂女足。"},{"pid":"2471d89c06a3e983b8f6b50d8c75f933f067d49a","tid":2185394,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T09:39:39.000Z","msg":"35m已經係最高身價<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad25e00d6a7d72f10f5c12971934e813d3aff716","tid":2185394,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T11:55:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb8b3c8073f53b5fc3d388b83a0dba59be1caef3","tid":2185394,"uid":188810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2471d89c06a3e983b8f6b50d8c75f933f067d49a","tid":2185394,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T09:39:39.000Z","msg":"35m已經係最高身價<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T11:59:13.000Z","msg":"0.35m (million)"},{"pid":"9b7dbb6f9ea16d4a655f12471ef29a605e657297","tid":2185394,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T12:00:26.000Z","msg":"<img